## Performance Best Practices

### Memoization

```typescript
import { useMemo, useCallback } from 'react'

// ✅ GOOD: Memoize expensive computations
const sortedMarkets = useMemo(() => {
  return markets.sort((a, b) => b.volume - a.volume)
